name: Bestromanticmovies
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: romantic movies
des:
This skill helps users to know the names of ten best romantic movies. People can get to know their names easily using this skill. This skill does not play or start a romantic movie on screen . 
Instead, it will just inform the names of ten best romantic movies.

After reaching the HELP prompt, please say : "Tell me ten romantic movies names " , to get the result.
Please listen to the device's instructions and follow the steps to get accurate result.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
